    "This type of feedback is usually generated based on pre-trained models.",
    "In specific, [62] proposes a self-refine mechanism.",
    "This mechanism consists of three crucial components: output, feedback, and refinement.",
    "Firstly, the agent generates an output.",
    "Then, it utilizes LLMs to provide feedback on the output and offer guidance on how to refine it."
